cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with image editing using textual descriptions, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) domains. The paper also proposes three different trainable models based on RNN and GAN, which involves machine learning techniques such as deep learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper investigates the use of Graph RNN, which is a graph-based neural network, to improve the performance of the filter bank model, which falls under the computer graphics (cs.GR) domain.
